18/02/2008
BRCKO, Bosnia and Herzegovina (BiH) -- Brcko Supervisor Raffi Gregorian dismissed two senior police officers -- Slobodan Katanic and Djordje Popovic -- on Saturday (February 16th), citing irresponsibility, falsifying documents and mismanagement.
Gregorian banned the two from working in any other public service capacity in Brcko.
(Dnevni Avaz - 17/02/08;
RTRS, SRNA, Fena - 16/02/08)
